<div class="patternContent"><div class="patternTopic"> <h1><a name="OSG_Software_Component_Certifica"></a> OSG Software Component: Certificate Scripts </h1>
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Purpose"></a> Purpose </span></h2>
<p />
The Certificate Scripts are a set of scripts that provide a command-line interface to the OSG PKI.
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Usage"></a> Usage </span></h2>
<p />
The certificate scripts are typically installed into /usr/bin and used by Grid Admins and others who need host certificates.
<p />
Detailed documentation is available at: <a href="https://twiki.grid.iu.edu/bin/view/Documentation/Release3/OSGPKICommandlineClients" target="_top">https://twiki.grid.iu.edu/bin/view/Documentation/Release3/OSGPKICommandlineClients</a>
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Source"></a> Source </span></h2>
<p />
OSG svn: <a href="https://vdt.cs.wisc.edu/svn/software/osg-cert-scripts-v3/" target="_top">https://vdt.cs.wisc.edu/svn/software/osg-cert-scripts-v3/</a>
<p />
Developer's guide: <a href="https://twiki.grid.iu.edu/bin/view/Operations/OSGPKICommandlineClientsDeveloperDocumentation" target="_top">https://twiki.grid.iu.edu/bin/view/Operations/OSGPKICommandlineClientsDeveloperDocumentation</a>
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Packaging"></a> Packaging </span></h2>
<p />
We distribute certificate scripts through the <a href="https://twiki.grid.iu.edu/bin/view/Documentation/Release3/OSGPKICommandlineClients#Installation" target="_top">OSG RPM repository</a>. 
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Design"></a> Design </span></h2>
<p />
[Brian Lin will add a technical design overview of the current (CILogon) OSG PKI infrastructure here. Include Wikipedia-style reference superscripts and include numbered reference links below.]
<p />
