</li> <li> <a href="http://osg-docdb.opensciencegrid.org/0011/001156/003/OSG-PKI-Transition-Final-Report-Jun27.pdf" target="_top">http://osg-docdb.opensciencegrid.org/0011/001156/003/OSG-PKI-Transition-Final-Report-Jun27.pdf</a>
