<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="History"></a> History </span></h2>
<p />
This component represents an evolution of the <a href="https://twiki.grid.iu.edu/twiki/bin/viewfile/Security/CSReadMe" target="_top">certificate scripts inherited from PPDG</a>.
<p />
The original OSG PKI Tools code was written at Indiana University under the lead of Von Welch; developers included Rohan Mathure and Viplav Khadke. The code was transitioned to the OSG Software team.
<p />
